gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nuggets 114, Bulls 106
gameRecap.excerpt: The Nuggets defeated the Bulls, 114-106. Reggie Jackson led the way with 25 points and six assists for the Nuggets, while Michael Porter Jr. added 17 points and seven rebounds in the victory. Coby White tallied 27 points, eight assists and five 3PM for the Bulls in the losing effort. The Nuggets improve to 16-9 on the season, while the Bulls fall to 9-16.
